snippet.title: Söldner-X 2: Final Prototype Gameplay #1
snippet.description:
http://www.soldner-x.com - Check out Söldner-X 2: Final Prototype for the PlayStation®3 system in action. Footage shown in this video is based on the first two stages of the game.

Söldner-X 2: Final Prototype will be available on the PlayStation®Store on May 25th, 2010. For more information, visit www.soldner-x.com.
